Vertigo - Bomb/Defuse

Counter-Terrorists: A new state building is being constructed, prevent the terriost from destroying the state building.

Terrorists: Our target is a state building. The Security is pretty low right now, since there isnt valueable information in the building yet. Plant the C4 on the toppest floor in the building.

Other Notes: There are 2 bomb targets in the mission.
